com.yahoo.bullet.dsl.deserializer

Class BulletDeserializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yahoo.bullet.dsl.deserializer.BulletDeserializer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AvroDeserializer, IdentityDeserializer, JavaDeserializer

    public abstract class BulletDeserializer
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A BulletDeserializer is used to deserialize or transform output from a BulletConnector into input for a BulletRecordConverter, e.g. from byte arrays to maps. Deserializers should extend this class and expect configuration though BulletDSLConfig.
